' Includes importantes
UC01 ..> UC09 : <<include>>
UC01 ..> UC13 : <<include>>
UC01 ..> UC10 : <<include>>
UC02 ..> UC01 : <<extend>>
UC05 ..> UC06 : <<extend>>

note right of UC01
  Caso de uso principal
  Tempo de início: < 2s
end note

